<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Paws & Tails</title>
</head>

<body>
    <!--Redirect users to a profile page instead!-->
    <%- include('../partials/nav') %>
        <% if (successFlash && successFlash.length) { %>
            <div class="flash-success bg-success text-white text-center fs-4 p-5">
                <%= successFlash[0] %>
            </div>
            <% } %>
                <div style="background-image: url(../top-img.jpg); background-position: center; background-size: cover; height: 100vh; position: relative;"
                    class="p-5">
                    <p style="position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 5%;" class="text-white fs-3 fst-italic">
                        Find the friend that
                    </p>
                    <p style="position: absolute; top: 55%; left: 5%;" class="text-white fs-3 fst-italic">
                        you've always wanted.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row d-flex align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-md-6 fs-2 text-center">
                            Do you...
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 fs-4 p-4">
                            <ul style="list-style-type: circle;">
                                <li>have a little bit of extra space in your home?</li>
                                <li>like the idea of sharing your lifestyle (and maybe a secret handshake)?</li>
                                <li>wish someone could come with you on longer trips?</li>
                                <li>enjoy being with yourself, but would like something extra?</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="carouselExampleAutoplaying" class="carousel slide bg-success-subtle p-5"
                    data-bs-ride="carousel">
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item mt-5 mb-5 active">
                            <p class="fs-4 fst-italic lh-lg text-center">
                                When I got Max from the pound, he just looked at me with those marbly eyes and a
                                masterful puppydog face.
                                Normally, I am immune to the I-am-cute thing from friends' pets, but
                                I was smitten the second my eyes met his.
                            </p>
                            <p class="fs-4">
                                - Darrel, 43
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item mt-5 mb-5">
                            <p class="fs-4 fst-italic lh-lg text-center">
                                I used to have bad nightmares from my time fighting overseas. Chica would always come to
                                my bed whenever she heard me
                                having an episode. Sometimes I even yelled at her for staring at me. But she always
                                stayed by my side.
                            </p>
                            <p class="fs-4">
                                - Conner, 32
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item mt-5 mb-5">
                            <p class="fs-4 fst-italic lh-lg text-center">
                                I can just do whatever I need to do and let her run around as she pleases. She comes
                                back around dinnertime and
                                lazes around the house. Sometimes she even sits with me while I read or watch TV. It's
                                like she wants to
                                spend time with me that way.
                            </p>
                            <p class="fs-4">
                                - Grace, 26
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleAutoplaying"
                        data-bs-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleAutoplaying"
                        data-bs-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div style="background-image: url(../banner-img.jpg); background-size: cover;" class="p-5">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Unforgettable Memories</h2>
                    <p class="fs-4 lh-lg">
                        We can all remember a time when a curious, fluffy face approached us and nestled its face
                        into our chest. We couldn't help but pet it! Pets bring the possibility of wonderful,
                        irreplaceable
                        memories. From childhood friends to service animals that aid those in need, having one of these
                        cute little furballs in your home definitely makes it feel more like a home!
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-success-subtle p-5">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Unconditional Love</h2>
                    <p class="fs-4 lh-lg">
                        Pets don't judge their owners based on their appearance, flaws, or mistakes.
                        They accept their human companions exactly as they are. Many even embrace them!
                        Even when a pet is scolded or disciplined, they tend to forgive and forget quickly.
                        They are there for their owners through good times and bad, offering comfort and support.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div style="background-image: url(../cover-img.jpg); background-size: cover;" class="p-5">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Better and Longer Life</h2>
                    <p class="fs-4 lh-lg">Studies have shown that owning a pet can have numerous health benefits for
                        their owners.
                        Interacting with pets can help reduce stress, lower blood pressure, and release endorphins
                        (feel-good
                        hormones) in the brain. Additionally, the companionship of a pet can reduce feelings of
                        loneliness and
                        depression, leading to improved mental well-being. The act of caring for a pet also encourages
                        physical
                        activity and can promote a sense of purpose and routine in a person's life.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide bg-success-subtle">
                    <div class="carousel-indicators">
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0"
                            class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1"
                            aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item text-center mt-5 mb-5 active">
                            <h2>Choose Team Cat if you:</h2>
                            <ul class="m-5 fs-4">
                                <li>Enjoy quiet weekends curled up with a book</li>
                                <li>Prefer independent pets that don't need as much attention</li>
                                <li>Like your pets to be really fluffy and cute</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item text-center mt-5 mb-5">
                            <h2>Choose Team Dog if you:</h2>
                            <ul class="m-5 fs-4">
                                <li>Need a more active and playful companion</li>
                                <li>Enjoy peace of mind by having an extra ear for danger</li>
                                <li>Want to take a friend on hiking trips</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
                        data-bs-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
                        data-bs-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="container p-2">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                                <img src="../home-cat.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="cat-pic" style="height: 600px;">
                                <div class="card-body fs-5">
                                    <h5 class="card-title text-center">Cats</h5>
                                    <p>Advantages:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Independent without much supervision</li>
                                        <li>Cute and fluffy fur is great for petting</li>
                                        <li>Said to have a sense for spiritual connections</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>Disadvantages:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Becomes less playful as time goes on</li>
                                        <li>Known to get stuck in tight or narrow spaces</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <!--Set up pathing later-->
                                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-success">Join Team Cat</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                                <img src="../home-dog.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="dog-pic" style="height: 600px;">
                                <div class="card-body fs-5">
                                    <h5 class="card-title text-center">Dogs</h5>
                                    <p>Advantages:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Playful, protective and fiercely loyal</li>
                                        <li>Great as companions on long trips</li>
                                        <li>Some breeds are natural hunters</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>Disadvantages:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Easily swayed by steaks and cookies</li>
                                        <li>Known to bark at dangerous plastic bags</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <!--Set up pathing later-->
                                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-success">Join Team Dog</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <footer class="bg-success-subtle p-2">
                    <p class="fs-5">&copy;Paws & Tails 2023</p>
                    <p>Photos by Charles Deluvio, Joe Caione, Raoul Droog, Milli and Andrew S. on Upsplash</p>
                </footer>
                <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
                    integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
                    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
                <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
                    integrity="sha384-BBtl+eGJRgqQAUMxJ7pMwbEyER4l1g+O15P+16Ep7Q9Q+zqX6gSbd85u4mG4QzX+"
                    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>